      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Akiba. ?] And then later, when I was in high school, there was a-- another one, only I rather like [INAUDIBLE] the way to-- you know, by this time we change the books from the year, from-- from that higher class to the lower class.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have been trying to help financially, because we have been doing so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't remember that name.",
