    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they give us the rifles, only five ammunition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was sent to the patrol, to the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] main station in Krakow, to-- to direct the people who were coming [INAUDIBLE], coming to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know how it is.",
